Calculator:

- UI
  - keyboard        --> Enter an expression using ht e keyboard buttons
  - display         --> Shows the expression entered
- InputController   --> Handles input enterd using the keyboard
- Processor         --> Calculates the expression entered via the keyboard



---------------- How to add aditonal program arguments programmatically
HashMap configProperties = new HashMap();
configProperties.put("fxConfigProperties", fxConfigProperties);

ParametersImpl parametersImpl = new ParametersImpl(configProperties, new String[] {"fxConfigProperties" });

ParametersImpl.registerParameters(this, parametersImpl);